  "flow": {
    "triggers": [
      {
        "id": "battery_mode_changed",
        "title": {
          "en": "Battery mode changed",
          "nl": "Batterijmodus is veranderd"
        },
        "tokens": [
          {
            "name": "mode",
            "type": "string",
            "title": {
              "en": "Mode",
              "nl": "Modus"
            },
            "example": {
              "en": "Self-Consumption"
            }
          }
        ],
        "args": [
          {
            "name": "device",
            "type": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=hione"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "actions": [
      {
        "id": "set_battery_mode",
        "title": {
          "en": "Set battery mode",
          "nl": "Stel batterijmodus in"
        },
        "titleFormatted": {
          "en": "Set battery mode to [[mode]]",
          "nl": "Stel batterijmodus in op [[mode]]"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Battery working mode. Self-Consumption: solar first, then battery, then grid. Economy: time-of-use schedule to avoid peak tariffs. Backup: only discharge during a grid outage. Off-Grid: no grid connection. Force Charge: forcibly charge to the set SoC — set Max Power to 0% to stop charging entirely, so the battery won't absorb power other sources feed back to the grid (e.g. other batteries discharging on high dynamic tariffs). Force Discharge: forcibly discharge to the set SoC. Peak Shaving: cap grid import at a set power. Time of Use: scheduled charge/discharge windows. Cloud connection required.",
          "nl": "Batterij-werkmodus. Eigen verbruik: eerst zon, dan batterij, dan net. Economie: tijdschema om piektarieven te vermijden. Noodstroom: ontlaadt alleen bij stroomuitval. Off-Grid: geen netaansluiting. Force Charge: laadt geforceerd tot de ingestelde SoC — zet Max vermogen op 0% om laden volledig te stoppen, zodat de Hoymiles geen stroom opneemt die andere bronnen terugleveren (bv. andere batterijen die ontladen bij hoge dynamische tarieven). Force Discharge: ontlaadt geforceerd tot de ingestelde SoC. Peak Shaving: begrenst netafname op een ingesteld vermogen. Time of Use: geplande laad-/ontlaadvensters. Cloudverbinding vereist."
        },
        "args": [
          {
            "name": "device",
            "type": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=hione"
          },
          {
            "name": "mode",
            "type": "dropdown",
            "title": {
              "en": "Mode",
              "nl": "Modus"
            },
            "values": [
              {
                "id": "1",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Self-Consumption",
                  "nl": "Eigen verbruik"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "2",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Economy",
                  "nl": "Economie"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "3",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Backup",
                  "nl": "Noodstroom"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "4",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Off-Grid",
                  "nl": "Off-Grid"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "5",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Force Charge",
                  "nl": "Force Charge (geforceerd laden)"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "6",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Force Discharge",
                  "nl": "Force Discharge (geforceerd ontladen)"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "7",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Peak Shaving",
                  "nl": "Pieksturing"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "8",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Time of Use",
                  "nl": "Tijdafhankelijk"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "set_reserve_soc",
        "title": {
          "en": "Set reserve SOC",
          "nl": "Stel reserve laadniveau in"
        },
        "titleFormatted": {
          "en": "Set reserve SOC to [[soc]]%",
          "nl": "Stel reserve laadniveau in op [[soc]]%"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Sets the minimum battery state of charge for the active battery mode (cloud connection required).",
          "nl": "Stelt het minimale laadniveau van de batterij in voor de actieve batterijmodus (cloudverbinding vereist)."
        },
        "args": [
          {
            "name": "device",
            "type": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=hione"
          },
          {
            "name": "soc",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "step": 1,
            "title": {
              "en": "Reserve SOC (%)",
              "nl": "Reserve laadniveau (%)"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "set_peak_shaving",
        "title": {
          "en": "Set Peak Shaving parameters",
          "nl": "Stel Pieksturing-parameters in"
        },
        "titleFormatted": {
          "en": "Set Peak Shaving: reserve [[reserve_soc]]%, max [[max_soc]]%, grid limit [[meter_power]]W",
          "nl": "Stel Pieksturing in: reserve [[reserve_soc]]%, max [[max_soc]]%, netgrens [[meter_power]]W"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Configures and activates Peak Shaving mode (cloud connection required).",
          "nl": "Configureert en activeert de Pieksturing-modus (cloudverbinding vereist)."
        },
        "args": [
          {
            "name": "device",
            "type": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=hione"
          },
          {
            "name": "reserve_soc",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "step": 1,
            "title": {
              "en": "Reserve SOC (%)",
              "nl": "Reserve laadniveau (%)"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "max_soc",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "step": 1,
            "title": {
              "en": "Max SOC (%)",
              "nl": "Max laadniveau (%)"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "meter_power",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 50000,
            "step": 100,
            "title": {
              "en": "Grid power limit (W)",
              "nl": "Netvermogensgrens (W)"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "set_relay",
        "title": {
          "en": "Switch dry contact",
          "nl": "Schakel droogcontact"
        },
        "titleFormatted": {
          "en": "Switch dry contact [[state]]",
          "nl": "Schakel droogcontact [[state]]"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Enables or disables the relay / dry contact output (cloud connection and compatible hardware required).",
          "nl": "Schakelt de relais-/droogcontactuitgang in of uit (cloudverbinding en geschikte hardware vereist)."
        },
        "args": [
          {
            "name": "device",
            "type": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=hione"
          },
          {
            "name": "state",
            "type": "dropdown",
            "title": {
              "en": "State",
              "nl": "Stand"
            },
            "values": [
              {
                "id": "on",
                "label": {
                  "en": "On",
                  "nl": "Aan"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "off",
                "label": {
                  "en": "Off",
                  "nl": "Uit"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "set_max_power",
        "title": {
          "en": "Set max power",
          "nl": "Stel max vermogen in"
        },
        "titleFormatted": {
          "en": "Set max charge/discharge power to [[power]]%",
          "nl": "Stel max laad/ontlaadvermogen in op [[power]]%"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Sets the charge/discharge power limit for Force Charge / Force Discharge mode (applies to the active mode if it is one of these, otherwise activates Force Charge). Tip: set to 0% in Force Charge to stop the battery from charging — useful to prevent it absorbing power that other sources feed back to the grid (e.g. other batteries discharging during high dynamic tariffs). Cloud connection required.",
          "nl": "Stelt de laad-/ontlaadvermogenslimiet in voor Force Charge / Force Discharge (past de actieve modus aan als dat een van deze is, anders wordt Force Charge geactiveerd). Tip: zet op 0% in Force Charge om laden van de batterij te stoppen — handig om te voorkomen dat de Hoymiles stroom opneemt die andere bronnen terugleveren (bv. andere batterijen die ontladen bij hoge dynamische tarieven). Cloudverbinding vereist."
        },
        "args": [
          {
            "name": "device",
            "type": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=hione"
          },
          {
            "name": "power",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "step": 1,
            "title": {
              "en": "Max power (%)",
              "nl": "Max vermogen (%)"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
