          "nl": "Time of Use: laden [[charge_from]]–[[charge_to]] op [[charge_power]]% tot [[charge_soc]]%, ontladen [[discharge_from]]–[[discharge_to]] op [[discharge_power]]% tot [[discharge_soc]]%"
